Patients Scenario
Amar was a banker and he had to meet with lots of
people as he was in his late 40's he was in more danger of getting
exposed to coronavirus and unfortunately, he got sick spent some days in
home isolation but his condition was not getting any better he was in
need of a ventilator but could not found bed or didn't even know what to
do next then he wen on play store and downloaded our app called COVID 19
safe app which first guided him how to keep himself safe and then he
moved to next features like finding the nearest the hospital most
importantly with available beds it even helps him in finding the
medicine which costs less compared to others
